    "commit": null,
    "change_date": "2020-12-15",
    "rationale": "GitHub Actions introduced environment protection rules with required reviewers. Previously, workflows would deploy directly to environments without manual approval. The new workflow adds multiple setup steps (s4-s6) to configure required reviewers and deployment approval steps (s8-s9) where designated reviewers must approve deployments before they proceed. This ensures critical deployments to production are reviewed by authorized team members.",
    "insertion_details": {
